Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section II, B (3) | Description :Audited Financial Statements covering one fiscal year shall befurnished to the Bank not later than 6 months | Due Date :30-Sep-2012

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section II, B (4) | Description :Not later than 3 months after effective date, the Borrower shallprepare and adopt terms of reference for the recruitment of Auditors | Due Date :17-Aug-2010

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section II, B (5)(a) | Description :Not later than 1 month after effective date the Borrower shallassign an additional internal audit staff to the internal audit unitof MWT | Due Date :17-Jun-2010
Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section II, B (5)(b) | Description :Not later than 1 month after effective date the Borrower shalldesignate staff in the accounts unit of MWT | Due Date :17-Jun-2010
